npc/sari: You made it through the first wave. Good.
npc/sari: Those creatures you fought used to be people. Office workers, students, parents. Online gambling took everything from them.
npc/sari: Let me teach you to recognise it, because it wears many faces.
npc/sari: Online slots — "slot gacor." Spin, lose, repeat. The most common, and the most addictive.
npc/sari: Sports betting — wagering on football and other matches. It hides behind a love of the game.
npc/sari: Online casino and poker — roulette, baccarat, cards — dressed up as if skill could save you.
npc/sari: "Togel" — online lottery and number bets.
npc/sari: And the sneakiest: fake "trading," binary options, and "investment" apps that are really just betting in a suit.
npc/sari: Different faces. One trick underneath — you risk real money on pure chance, and the odds are set against you.
npc/sari: Did you notice how the Adbots flash in patterns? Real gambling apps use the exact same lights and sounds to fool your brain.
npc/sari: "Free credits." "Guaranteed jackpot." All of it is bait. The house ALWAYS wins. By design.
npc/sari: Clear eyes. That is your strongest weapon out here.
